Package com.cisco.pxgrid.samples.ise

Contains classes that demonstrate how to use the pxGrid Java SDK.

See: Description

    ANCActions  
    ANCNotificationHandlers
    This class holds all ANC Notification Handlers for subscribe

    ANCNotificationHandlers.DeletePolicyNotificationHandler  
    ANCNotificationHandlers.UpdatePolicyNotificationHandler  
    CapabilityQuery
    Demonstrates how to use a pxGrid client to query controller for all capabilities.

    EndpointProfileMetaDataQuery  
    EndpointProfileMetaDataSubscribe  
    EndpointProfileMetaDataSubscribe.SampleNotificationCallback  
    EPSQuarantine
    Demonstrates how to use a pxGrid client to invoke an Endpoint Protection Service (EPS) quarantine by IP address in ISE.
    EPSUnquarantine
    Demonstrates how to use a pxGrid client to invoke an Endpoint Protection Service (EPS) unquarantine by MAC address in ISE.
    GenericClient  
    MultiGroupClient
    Sample to demonstrate a client is able to perform actions on multiple topics Creates ANC policy which requires client to have ANC group auth Queries Session Directory for a given IP which requires Session group auth Client should have both ANC and Session group membership
    ProposeCapability
    Demonstrates how to use a pxGrid client to propose a new capability to pxGrid administrator.
    ProposeCapability.SampleNotificationCallback  
    SampleHelper  
    SessionCache
    A cache of active sessions.
    SessionDownload
    Demonstrates how to use download all active sessions from ISE
    SessionQueryByIp
    Demonstrates how to query ISE for an active session by IP address
    SessionSubscribe
    Demonstrates how to subscribe to session notifications generated by ISE
    SessionSubscribe.SampleNotificationHandler  
    SessionSubscribeDownload
    Demonstrates how to use an xGrid client to subscribe to and download all active sessions from ISE automatically upon Grid Connection (automation is sustainable upon a ReconnectionManager reconnect).
    SXPBindingDownload
    Demonstrates how to use download all active sessions from ISE
    SXPBindingSubscribe  
    SXPBindingSubscribe.SampleNotificationHandler  
    TrustSecMetaDataQuery  
    TrustSecMetaDataSubscribe  
    TrustSecMetaDataSubscribe.SampleNotificationCallback  
    UserIdentityGroupDownload
    Demonstrates how to download all identity groups in ISE
    UserIdentityGroupQuery
    Demonstrates how to use an xGrid client to query an identity group.
    UserIdentityGroupSubscribe
    Demonstrates how to use an xGrid client to subscribe to identity group notifications.
